# Version control
.git
.gitignore

# Node
node_modules
**/node_modules
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Build outputs
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo

# Go build artifacts
**/bin
**/*.exe
**/*.test

# Environment files (never bake secrets into images)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Editor & OS
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Infra (not needed in app images)
infra/

# Docs
**/*.md
